'''Edward Silvio Emery''' is an [[United States|American]] politician.

In 1976, 1978, and 1980, Emery ran as an independent against [[United States House of Representatives|U.S. Rep.]] [[Thomas W. L. Ashley]] ([[United States Democratic Party|D]]-[[Ohio]]). Each time, Emery came in a distant third in the race.

In 1998 and 2002, Emery was the nominee of the [[Republican Party (United States)|Republican party]] to contest the incumbency of [[Marcy Kaptur]]. Emery lost both these races.

In October 2003, Emery dressed as [[Arnold Schwarzenegger]] at a Halloween Party sponsored by the Greater Toledo Republican Club.<ref name="halloween">
