In 2004, Emery lost his bid for the Republican nomination to [[Larry A. Kaczala]].

Emery is again seeking the Republican nomination against [[Marcy Kaptur]] in 2006. He faces Bradley S. Leavitt and Dirk Kubala in the May 2nd primary election. <ref name="election">
